Andri's Main Loop

Goals:
 * Portability
 * Utility
 * Simplicity

Non-goals:
 * MS Windows (TM) support
 * Solving the C10K problem

Features:
 * File descriptor event handlers
 * Timers
 * Tickers
 * Signal handlers
 * Idle dispatch callbacks
 * Thread pool
 * Interoperability with other event loops

WWW: https://github.com/any1/aml
